ntention is that `@tag` aligns to the top `Description`.\r\n\r\n**Parameter description alignment**\r\nTabs between `@tag {type} name` and `description` to align descriptions ([example in Preact](https://github.com/developit/preact/blob/4f57ba02bd4dee37d3278f2e75ce18073a36deac/src/vdom/component.js#L13)):\r\n```js\r\n/**\r\n * Description\r\n * @param {Object} props\tDescription\r\n * @param {Number} props2\tDescription2\r\n */\r\n```\r\n\r\nSingle space between `@tag {type} name` (i.e. don't align descriptions) ([example in Preact](https://github.com/developit/preact/blob/4f57ba02bd4dee37d3278f2e75ce18073a36deac/src/vdom/index.js#L40))\r\n```js\r\n/**\r\n * Description\r\n * @param {Object} props Description\r\n * @param {Number} props2 Description2\r\n */\r\n```\r\n\r\n@developit @marvinhagemeister - let me know if you have an opinion or not - it doesn't matter to me. I just wanted to see if it matters to you.","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/developit/preact/issues/1105","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/developit/preact","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/developit/preact/issues/1105/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/developit/preact/issues/1105/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/developit/preact/issues/1105/events","html_url":"https://github.com/developit/preact/issues/1105","id":324065530,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUzMjQwNjU1MzA=","number":1105,"title":"External API methods for a component","user":{"login":"DataTables","id":278219,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI3ODIxOQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/278219?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/DataTables","html_url":"https://github.com/DataTables","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DataTables/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DataTables/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DataTables/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.c